Meran. White's development plan included the quiet development of the
dark-square bishop on b2. However, nowadays, after 6.Qc2 Bd6 (the most common
Black's reply), White has a very interesting and reliable gambit at his
disposal: 7.g4.   6...} b6 $5 {[%csl Gg7][%cal Yf8g7] By this move, Black
